edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.entity

Class Input

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.entity.Input

  • public class Input
extends Object
    This class is an Entity class for the RoomDatabase specifically for the avaiable inputs to decide what choices you are presented in your choose your own adventure game. The Entity has ForeignKey to the Player by their id, and to the Scene the game is currently at by id. Each Input has an id, name of what the ClarifaiTask found from the CameraFragment's picture turned into a List of Strings.
    Author:
    Brian Alexander
